<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@100..900&family=Quattrocento:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Quattrocento", serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #bb9e44 0%, #9d842e 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .content-section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .content-section:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .content-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #bb9e44;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .key-features {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .key-features h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #bb9e44;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .key-features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .key-features li {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }

        .key-features li:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #bb9e44;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .key-features li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .testimonial {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 700px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .testimonial p {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .testimonial h5 {
            color: #bb9e44;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="logo" class="d-inline-block align-text-top">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto">
                    <% navLinks.forEach(function(link) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-uppercase fw-bold <%= link.url === '/about' ? 'active' : '' %>" href="<%= link.url %>"><%= link.text %></a>
                        </li>
                    <% }); %>
                </ul>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-custom me-2">BOOK NOW</a>
                    <% if (locals.isAuthenticated) { %>
                        <a href="/api/logout" class="btn btn-custom">LOGOUT</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-custom">LOGIN</a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Vistora</h1>
            <p>Where Heritage Meets Luxury</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Welcome to Vistora</h2>
        <p>At Vistora, we pride ourselves on offering unparalleled luxury and world-class hospitality. From opulent rooms and suites to exquisite dining and rejuvenating spa experiences, we ensure that every moment of your stay is memorable.</p>
        <p>Our properties are located in some of the most picturesque destinations, each designed to offer a unique experience that blends modern comfort with timeless elegance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section container">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>Founded in 1985, Vistora began as a boutique hotel and has since grown into a globally recognized brand. Over the decades, we have hosted countless travelers, dignitaries, and celebrities, earning a reputation for excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section container">
        <h2>Our Vision and Mission</h2>
        <p>Our vision is to set the benchmark for luxury hospitality worldwide. We aim to create memorable experiences for our guests through innovation, dedication, and passion.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="key-features container">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Luxurious Rooms and Suites</li>
            <li>Gourmet Dining Experiences</li>
            <li>State-of-the-Art Spa and Wellness Facilities</li>
            <li>Event and Conference Spaces</li>
            <li>Personalized Guest Services</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section container">
        <h2>Guest Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"Vistora exceeded all our expectations. The attention to detail and the level of service were unparalleled. We can’t wait to come back!"</p>
            <h5>- Sarah Williams</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"The spa and dining experience were phenomenal. Truly a home away from home with luxury at its best."</p>
            <h5>- David Thompson</h5>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <% footerSections.forEach(function(section) { %>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <h5><%= section.title %></h5>
                        <% if (section.type === 'text') { %>
                            <p><%= section.content %></p>
                        <% } else if (section.type === 'links') { %>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <% section.links.forEach(function(link) { %>
                                    <li><a href="<%= link.url %>"><%= link.text %></a></li>
                                <% }); %>
                            </ul>
                        <% } else if (section.type === 'contact') { %>
                            <% section.items.forEach(function(item) { %>
                                <p><%= item %></p>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } else if (section.type === 'social') { %>
                            <% section.icons.forEach(function(icon) { %>
                                <a href="<%= icon.url %>"><i class="bi <%= icon.class %> me-2"></i></a>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom mt-4">
                <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
                <ul class="list-inline">
                    <% footerLinks.forEach(function(link) { %>
                        <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="<%= link.url %>"><%= link.text %></a></li>
                    <% }); %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
